Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,General.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ducal Minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you were about to betroth Diāochán to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you send her to the Grand Preceptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,General! Please, calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that you sent Diāochán in a carriage\Nto the Premier's mansion as a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:14.26,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(267.955,720)\fade(255,0,255,0,510,2345,2700)}Wáng Yǔn\NStyled: Zishī
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't know this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, in court,\N the Grand Preceptor told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll come to your household tomorrow, \N I have something to discuss."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So I prepared a small feast for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,While he was drinking, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"I heard you have a daughter named Diāochán"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"that you betrothed to my son, Fèngxiān."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:43.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(206.591,679.091)\fade(255,0,255,0,490,2150,2620)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled: Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was afraid it was undecided,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"so I'm here to confirm and meet her as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I led Diāochán to greet the Grand Preceptor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said, "Today is a good day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Allow me to take this girl to marry Fèngxiān."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, General,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the Grand Preceptor came to pick her up in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I dare refuse him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to send my daughter over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have troubled you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you my humblest apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you didn't know, \Nwhat's there to apologize for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Grand Preceptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Preceptor is sleeping with his new bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't got up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Which new bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl named Diāochán.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Diāochán?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(497.046,662.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,490,1980,2180)}Diāochán
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān, my son! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(261.818,722.045)\fade(255,0,255,0,495,2555,5555)}Dǒng Zhuō\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to desire my mistress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here! You are forbidden to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's present?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Preceptor sent this servant to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the Marquis of Wēn from\N now on can enter his mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it was your own home, \Nno need to be formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That senile lech!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He dares to mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General, why aren't you in court \Nwith the Grand Preceptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe to talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You may first go to\NFèngyí Pavillion and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,General, though I am not\NDucal Minister Wáng's natural daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he treats me like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell for you at first sight, my general.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So he betrothed me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped I could depend on you all my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:10:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but the lecherous Grand Preceptor deflowered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill myself there only\Nbecause I wanted to say farewell to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have to live with this humiliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily today, I was able \Nto see you General.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My body has been defiled. \NI cannot be with you any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish you see me one last time, general!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long known your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I only regret not being together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be your wife in this life. \NWe'll have to meet in the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I cannot marry you in this life,\Nthen I am no hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, a day here is like a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I force a smile before him and weep behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take pity, General! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Fèngxiān been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the inner hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I've come unannounced,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,fearing the old lech will see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you are so afraid of that old lech,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will never get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me time, I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Diāochán at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the garden admiring the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in my boudoir, \NI heard of your great name
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,like thunder piercing the ears.\NI thought you were the greatest hero of this era,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead, even you \Nare controlled by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've.. I've came to your mansion\N when I learnt that you were furious
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and went straight to the\N back garden to look for Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I came and saw Lǚ Bù escaping. He was shouting, {\i1}"The Grand Preceptor wants to kill me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've rushed here to mediate peace\N but accidentally bumped into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard whelp! He has the guts to have an affair with my mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Grand Preceptor, \Ncalm down! That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1210.909,568.636)\fade(255,0,255,0,590,2820,3180)}Lǐ Rú
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:15:00.34,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: King Zhuāng of Chǔ was one of the Five Hegemons of the Spring and Autumn period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Sir, of old, King Zhuāng of Chǔ hosted a feast with his retainers one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}When the candle was out, Jiǎng Xióng took advantage to flirt with the queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}but the queen ripped the tassel from his hat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and asked King Zhuāng of Chǔ to light the candle to reveal the offender,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}but King Zhuāng of Chǔ ordered all the retainers to remove their tassels
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}so the lights wouldn't indicate the offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}After King Zhuāng of Chǔ was surrounded by Qín troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Jiǎng Xióng risked his life to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}At present, Diāochán is merely just a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and Lǚ Bù is your most trusted and fierce general.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Grand Preceptor, if you can seize this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and give Diāochán to Lǚ Bù,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Lǚ Bù will remember this kindness and will definitely repay you with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Consider the advantages.\NI hope that sir understands this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Slut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare have an affair with Lǚ Bù?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor, I was only admiring \Nthe flowers in the garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when Lǚ Bù suddenly came. \NI wanted to avoid him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said, "I am the Grand Preceptor's son. \NWhy must you avoid me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With these words, he forced me to Fèngyí Pavilion with his halberd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he had no good intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was afraid he'd assail me and disgrace you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I intended to drown myself in the lotus pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But he held me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was between life and death \Nwhen you came and saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I were to send you to Lǚ Bù?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I would rather die than be disgraced!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Lǐ Rú's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a profound friendship with Lǚ Bù
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so he set up this plan regardless of your honor, and my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have the heart to give you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you love me dearly,\N I'm afraid we cannot stay here for long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or Lǚ Bù will certainly hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:16.14,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Méiwù(郿坞) was Dong Zhuo's real-life fortified manor, located 250 lǐ from Chang'an.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we'll live together in my Méiwù-manor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can enjoy a joyful life there,\N carefree and without worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor, today is a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can send Diāochán to Fèngxiān now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lǚ Bù and I are father and son!\NIt's improper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ignore his crimes, nevermind them. \NYou can go reassure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor, you can't be fooled by that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to give your concubine to Lǚ Bù or not? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not talk about Diāochán ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who speaks of this again will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,All of us will die in the hands of that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,General! General!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day I caught a cold, so I couldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I haven't seen you for a long time, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, the Grand Preceptor rode to Méiwù-manor,\N I had to see him off despite my illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask why you are sighing, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this time, the Grand Preceptor \Nstill hasn't sent my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That lech has kept her for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I even start!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we discuss this in my humble abode. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined that the Grand Preceptor\Ncould do something this barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He has not only defiled my daughter, \Nbut took your wife as a concubine, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be the ridicule of the whole nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not laughing at \Nthe Grand Preceptor, but at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not whether I am \Nridiculed as senile or incompetent,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're the peerless hero of the realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:24:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you bear such a humiliation and shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for letting these\N words slip, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill that senile wretch! Avenge my disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,General, General!\NDon't get into trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.02,0:24:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A real man should stand up\N between Heaven and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I submit to him any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a great general,\Nhow could the Grand Preceptor restrain you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.31,0:24:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will butcher that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.64,0:24:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.42,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I have a father and son bond,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear what later generations will say about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,General, your surname is Lǚ, \Nbut his surname is Dǒng.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.42,0:25:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider this:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.06,0:25:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At Fèngyí Pavillion, when he threw your halberd at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,where was the bond then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.40,0:25:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if not for your words, I would be amiss
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you can revive the Imperial House of Hàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.40,0:25:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be known as a loyal officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and your name will be \Nimmortalized in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.10,0:25:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you aid Dǒng Zhuó...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.26,0:25:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be known as a traitor, \Nand go down in history as a byword of infamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros and cons, advantages and disadvantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.76,0:26:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To be pure or impure, to be loyal or disloyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.40,0:26:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please consider this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your words have cleared my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.46,0:26:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am determined! \NDo not doubt me sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.20,0:26:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.34,0:26:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.16,0:26:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just that if our plan fails, we will be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.84,0:26:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I swear to revive the Hàn state by killing the national traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.18,0:26:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}If I ever betray my word,\Nthen doom me for all of eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.75,0:27:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.24,0:27:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}If the House of Hàn doesn't fall, it's thanks to you, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.90,0:27:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Please accept my respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.42,0:27:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.72,0:27:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Does the Excellency of the Masses have any plans to eliminate the traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.94,0:27:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I'll tell you it when the time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.64,0:27:53.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuō is far away in Méiwù-manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.64,0:28:01.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We could send an eloquent man to Méiwù asking him to come to court to discuss matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.10,0:28:07.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but who to send?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.53,0:28:12.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Lǐ Sù was originally one of Dǒng Zhuó's supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.30,0:28:18.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He once enticed Lǚ Bù to kill Dīng Yuán \Nbut Dǒng Zhuó did not promote him afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.92,0:28:20.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He harbors a grudge due to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:25.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If we send Lǐ Sù,\Nthat traitor won't be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.14,0:28:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sires.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.17,0:28:35.44,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(220.909,644.318)}Lǐ Sù
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.16,0:28:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Exalted sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.86,0:28:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.62,0:28:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.93,0:29:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sù, back then, you induced me to kill Dīng Jiànyáng and turn to Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.50,0:29:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this lech abuses the Emperor\Nand oppresses the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His sins are innumerable and all of us share resentment!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Ducal Minister asks you, Brother Sù,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.82,0:29:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,send an imperial edict to Méiwù biding Dǒng Zhuō to enter the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pretend to be subservient while the warriors wait within the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.30,0:29:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,By killing this traitor, we would help the Hàn Empire and we'll be known as loyal ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.19,0:29:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your honorable opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.92,0:29:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, exalted Excellency of the Masses!\N Thank you, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.83,0:29:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long wanted to kill that traitor Dǒng!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I only regret I wasn't able to find any allies.\NNow we have been
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.90,0:29:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,bestowed an opportunity by heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.12,0:29:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.18,0:30:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please go straight to Méiwù-manor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.05,0:30:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}My dear concubine, I dreamt \Nof a dragon covering my body last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.82,0:30:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Sure enough, good news came today when
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.58,0:30:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}the Son of Heaven sent for me to enter the court
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.28,0:30:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and abdicate the throne to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.58,0:30:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Excellency of the Masses Wáng \Nhas already built an abdication platform for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.56,0:30:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}They're just waiting for me to accept the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.32,0:30:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}After I become the Son of Heaven,\N you will be my favored concubine!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.78,0:31:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your great favor, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.40,0:31:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful girl, you just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.12,0:31:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to take you to the palace soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.26,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}The carriage's wheel broke\Nand the horse escaped its reins,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.98,0:31:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}what omens do they bode?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.28,0:31:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}My lord, it bodes you will ascend the throne,\Nabandon the old for the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}These omens mean you will ride in the Emperor's jade carriage on a golden saddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.01,0:31:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavens really blessed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.28,0:32:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)\i1}The grass spreads a thousand lǐ, how green it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.85,0:32:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)\i1}Within ten days divine, it won't be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.88,0:32:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The grass spreads a thousand lǐ, how green it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.72,0:32:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that song bode well or ill fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.40,0:32:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It bodes the Liú clan will be gone and Dǒng clan will thrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.66,0:32:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop singing! Stop singing!\NGo play over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.22,0:32:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.55,0:32:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the song means?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.65,0:32:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)\i1}'Thousand lǐ grass' {\i0}refers to the word{\i1} 'Dǒng'{\i0},\N{\i1}'Ten days divine'{\i0} refers to the word{\i1} 'Zhuó',{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.50,0:32:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}It means that Dǒng Zhuó won't live!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.30,0:32:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}You want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.66,0:33:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven blesses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.78,0:33:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven blesses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.15,0:33:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven blesses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My respects, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.78,0:34:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright! It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.00,0:34:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.92,0:34:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After I accept the Emperor's abdication,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.24,0:34:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be in charge of all the military forces throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.08,0:34:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.06,0:34:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't Wáng Yǔn and Lǐ Rú here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.76,0:34:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wáng Yǔn is on the abdication platform waiting for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.98,0:35:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǐ Rú caught an illness, so he could not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.06,0:35:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son respectfully invites you, father, \Nto ascend the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.50,0:35:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.58,0:35:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.86,0:36:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The traitor scum has arrived! \NSummon the warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.77,0:36:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my son Fèngxiān?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.40,0:36:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the imperial order! Kill the treacherous vassal Dǒng Zhuó! The rest will be pardoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.36,0:36:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān, my son! Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.97,0:36:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Old bastard! We cannot coexist together!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.02,0:36:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
